works.description: Designed by Andrea Crosetta, the new BB fireplace from Antrax Art heating is sure to be the center of attention in any home. The BB, as in Baby Bubble or Brigitte Bardot, is a bioethanol fireplace with an open combustion chamber and inimitable oval and clover-shaped openings. You can choose the BB fireplace from among 200 colors to complement your décor. The wall-mounted fireplace uses a bioethanol burner that keeps the fireplace to low temperatures of around 75° C, just like a radiator
